        public TableOfContentsMacro.Builder separator(String separator)
        Set a custom separator. Each item is separated by the value you enter. You can enter any text as a separator, for example "***". If using a custom separator, be aware that text displays exactly as entered, with no additional white space to further separate the characters.
        Parameters:
